column2: linoroso Paring Knife 3.5 inch Small Kitchen Knife with Elegant Gift Box, Sharp Forged German Carbon Stainless Steel Fruit Knife, Full Tang, Ergonomic Handle-Classic Series
column3:
Linoroso Paring Knife - 3.5 Inch Small Kitchen Knife with Elegant Gift Box

The Linoroso Paring Knife is a premium kitchen tool designed for precision cutting. Crafted from imported expertly forged German ThyssenKrupp high carbon stainless steel, it boasts exceptional durability and sharpness. The blade, with a Rockwell hardness scale of 56+, is hand polished to a precise 11-12 degrees per side, ensuring maximum sharpness and edge retention.

Chromium integration into the stainless steel enhances its robustness, durability, and resistance to rust and corrosion. The carefully tapered blade offers improved hardness, flexibility, and minimal slicing resistance, making it perfect for tasks like garnishing, mincing, peeling, slicing, and dicing.

The ergonomic handle provides optimum comfort, control, and agility. The full tang and forged bolster create a perfect balance between the blade and handle, allowing for extended use without fatigue. The handle's unique ergonomic design ensures a comfortable grip.

This paring knife comes in a premium elegant gift box, making it an ideal gift for weddings, birthdays, housewarmings, and more. It is a reliable and trusted kitchen tool for all your cutting needs. For any questions or suggestions, feel free to contact us.

  • Blade Material: High Carbon Stainless Steel
  • Brand: Linoroso
  • Color: Black
  • Handle Material: Stainless Steel
  • Blade Edge: Plain
  • Blade Length: 3.5 Inches

column3:
Linoroso Professional Chef's Knife

Experience precision and durability with the Linoroso Professional Chef's Knife, crafted for both professional chefs and home cooks. Designed to be multi-functional, this knife handles cutting, dicing, slicing, chopping, and deboning with ease. Its ultra-sharp, corrosion-resistant blade ensures flawless performance every time.

Key Features

  • High-Carbon Stainless Steel Blade: Crafted from premium stainless steel with 0.6–0.75% carbon, this blade is two times harder than standard knives, ensuring exceptional sturdiness and long-lasting sharpness.
  • Multi-functional Knife: Designed as a gyutou multipurpose knife, it excels at cutting, slicing, chopping, dicing, and even deboning. Its HRC rating of 56–58 ranks it among the toughest in its class.
  • Ergonomic Pakka Handle: The comfortable, durable Pakka handle minimizes hand fatigue and finger numbness during extended use. This African-origin material offers superior strength and stability for professional performance.
  • Ultra-sharp Edge: Utilizing advanced Japanese engineering, the razor-sharp edge provides precision cuts and remains sharp even after heavy use.
  • Corrosion-Resistant Blade: Featuring 16–18% chrome in its metal composition, the blade resists tarnishing and maintains a glossy, professional finish over time.

Perfect for Any Occasion

This Linoroso Chef's Knife makes an ideal gift for Halloween, Christmas, weddings, and birthdays. Backed by a lifetime warranty and a no-hassle refund policy within the first 3 months, your satisfaction is guaranteed.

Learn More

Customer Reviews
